    <summary>The Microsoft ODBC Driver for SQL Server 17 is a software component that enables applications to connect and interact with Microsoft SQL Server databases</summary>
    <description>
    *This package is for the older, Microsoft ODBC Driver for SQL Server 17*

    The Microsoft ODBC Driver for SQL Server 17 is a software component designed to facilitate connectivity between applications and Microsoft SQL Server databases. 
    This driver adheres to the Open Database Connectivity (ODBC) standard, providing a unified interface for developers across different programming languages and platforms. 
    By using this driver, applications can establish reliable and efficient connections to SQL Server databases, enabling seamless data access, retrieval, and manipulation.
